!!!5
%html{class:"no-js", lang:"es"} 
	%head
		%meta{charset:"utf-8"}
		%title La mejor comida en Restaurante Facilito
		%meta{name:"description", content:"Come rico en el mejor restaurante de la ciudad, servicio de primera."}
		%link{rel:'stylesheet', href:'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Dancing+Script', type:'text/css'}
		%link{rel:"stylesheet", href:"css/normalize.css"}
		%link{rel:"stylesheet", href:"css/bootstrap.css"}
		%link{rel:"stylesheet", href:"css/flexboxgrid.min.css"}
		%link{rel:"stylesheet", href:"css/style.css"}
		%meta{name:"viewport", content:"width=device-width, initial-scale=1"}
		%meta{:"data-name" => "image-counter", content:"#{gallery_images.size - 1}"}
		%script{src:"js/vendor/modernizr-2.8.3.min.js"}
	%body
		="<!--[if lt IE 9]>"
		%p{class:"browserupgrade"}
			Estás usando un navegador 
			%strong desactualizado.
			Por favor
			%a{href:"http://browserhappy.com/"}
				actualiza tu navegador 
			para una mejor experiencia
		="<![endif]-->"
		.video-container
			%video{autoplay:true,loop:true,width:"1280",heigiht:"720"}
				%source{src:"/videos/mp4/bbq.mp4",typ:"video/mp4",poster:"/videos/images/bbq.jpg"}
				%source{src:"/videos/webm/bbq.webm",typ:"video/webm"}
		.row.full-height.middle-xs.center-xs.relative.up#home
			.col-xs-12
				.box.white-text
					%img{src:"/imgs/logo.png", width:200}
					%h1.dancing-script.title.no-margin Restaurante Facilito
					%p#is-open 
						%i.glyphicon.glyphicon-time
						Abierto Ahora
			%nav.fixed.top.right.navigation.white-text#navigation
				-menu = ["Home", "Menú", "Galería", "Contacto", "Cómo llegar"]
				%ul.list-inline
					-menu.each do |item|
						%li
							%a{}= item
			.absolute.black.large-padding.left.white-text.full-width#description
				.row.middle-xs.center-xs
					.col-xs-7.col-sm-6.white-text.medium
						Atención cálida y comida preparada por artistas
					.col-xs#sticky-navigation
						.box
							%nav.text-right.navigation#responsive-nav
								%i.glyphicon.glyphicon-menu-hamburger.white-text.subtitle.glyphicon-remove#menu-opener
								%ul.list-inline
									-menu.each do |item|
										%li
											%a{}= item
	.text-center.relative#menu
		.absolute.white#menu-title
			%h2.dancing-script.title Menú
		-menu_photos = [{name: "Club Sandwich", pricing:"10.00", image: "club-sandwich"},{name: "Combo Hamburguesa", pricing:"50.00", image: "combo"},{name: "Hamburguesa", pricing:"20.00", image: "hamburger"},{name: "Hot cakes", pricing:"30.00", image: "hot-cakes"},{name: "Panini", pricing:"15.00", image: "panini"},{name: "Papas", pricing:"10.00", image: "papas"},{name: "Club Sandwich", pricing:"10.00", image: "club-sandwich"},{name: "Hamburguesa", pricing:"20.00", image: "hamburger"}]
		
		.row
			-menu_photos.each do |photo|
				.col-md-4.col-lg-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.food{style:"background-image:url(/imgs/food/#{photo[:image]}-thumb.jpg)"}
					.screen
						.row.middle-xs.full-height
							.col-xs-12.white-text
								%h3.dancing-script.subtitle= photo[:name]
								%p.no-margin= photo[:pricing] + "USD"
	#gallery
		.inner
			-gallery_images.each do |image|
				.image{style:"background-image:url(/imgs/food/#{image}.jpg);"}
	.container
		.card.white.black-text.text-center.relative
			%h3.medium.slim
				En
				%strong.dancing-script.medium Restaurante Facilito
				cocinar no es una profesión, no es una técnica, es un
				%strong.dancing-script.medium arte
			%p.top-space
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies nec, pellentesque eu, pretium quis, sem. Nulla consequat massa quis enim. Donec pede justo, fringilla vel, aliquet nec, vulputate eget, arcu. In enim justo, rhoncus ut, imperdiet a, venenatis vitae, justo. Nullam dictum felis eu pede mollis pretium. Integer tincidunt. Cras dapibus. Vivamus elementum semper nisi. Aenean vulputate eleifend tellus. Aenean leo ligula, porttitor eu, consequat vitae, eleifend ac, enim. 
				%strong.dancing-script.medium Coco - Chef
				.large-padding.medium.black.white-text.text-center
					También puedes acceder a este sitio sin conexión a internet.

	.black.white-text.full-height#contact
		.row.middle-xs.full-height
			.col-xs-12
				.box
					%p.text-center.medium#info-contacto Presiona enter para llenar el campo correspondiente y enviarnos un correo.
					%form{action:"https://formspree.io/cejaramillof@gmail.com",method:"POST",id:"contact-form",class:"step-form"}
						.row.center-xs
							.col-xs-12.col-md-2.col-md-1.first-sm
								.box
									-3.times do |i|
										-if i == 0
											.path-step.active
										-else
											.path-step
							.col-xs-12.col-sm-3.first-xs
								.box
									%fieldset.step.active
										%input{type:"email",name:"email",placeholder:"Tu correo",class:"input",required:true}
									%fieldset.step
										%input{type:"text",name:"name",placeholder:"Tu nombre",class:"input",required:true}
									%fieldset.step
										%textarea{name:"body",placeholder:"Escribe tu mensaje..",class:"input",required:true}
	#location
		#map
		#message.black.large-padding.white-text.text-center.medium

										
	%script{src:"http://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.0.min.js", integrity:"sha256-cCueBR6CsyA4/9szpPfrX3s49M9vUU5BgtiJj06wt/s=", crossorigin:"anonymous"}
	%script
		window.jQuery || document.write("<script src='/js/vendor/jquery-1.12.0.min.js'><\/script>")
	%script{src:"https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyD14F9HQeo3uyGj7GJQiHPg5v1bIgBdBXw"}
	%script{src:"/dist/maps.js"}
	%script{src:"/dist/form_object.js"}
	%script{src:"/dist/main.js"}
	%script{src:"/dist/step.js"}
